description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20MIN full body pilates workout // hourglass sculpt & strengthen | LIDIAVMERA' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: a peaceful and energising 20 minutes of movement! 

Hope you have fun doing this workout!
